             took his Money, and the other Shrimpton his Whip, and the third Man, was of the size of Drummond. That one of them said , D - n you, yours is a good Horse, that he desiring them not to take his Horse; they reply
               <persName id="t17300228-70-person390">
                  'd, D<interp inst="t17300228-70-person390" type="given" value="'d"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t17300228-70-person390" type="gender" value="indeterminate"></interp>
